pel de Car-Vex en Man of Steel de 2013. Ha aparecido en varios proyectos desde estos, y en 2021 interpretó a Chambers en Army of the Dead de Zack Snyder.","name":"","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"CN","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"萨曼莎·温（Samantha Win，原名萨曼莎·乔，1991年3月29日-）是加拿大女演员和武术家，曾代表加拿大参加2005-2008年国际武术锦标赛。2008年，她作为加拿大队的一员参加了2008年北京武术锦标赛。2012 年，她在《真人快打：遗产》中饰演 Kitana 一角，随后在 2013 年的《钢铁之躯》中饰演 Car-Vex。此后，她出现在各种项目中，并于 2021 年在扎克·施奈德的《亡灵军团》中扮演钱伯斯。","name":"萨曼莎·温","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"RU","iso_639_1":"ru","name":"Pусский","english_name":"Russian","data":{"biography":"","name":"Саманта Вин","primary":false}},{"iso_3166_1":"HK","iso_639_1":"zh","name":"普通话","english_name":"Mandarin","data":{"biography":"薩曼莎·温（Samantha Win，原名薩曼莎·喬，1991 年 3 月 29 日-）是加拿大女演員和武術家，曾代表加拿大參加 2005 - 2008 年國際武術錦標賽。2008 年，她作為加拿大隊的一員參加了 2008 年北京武術錦標賽。2012 年，她在《真人快打：遺產》中飾演 Kitana 一角，隨後在 2013 年的《鋼鐵之軀》中飾演 Car - Vex。此後，她出現在各種項目中，並於 2021 年在紮克·施奈德的《亡靈軍團》中扮演錢伯斯。","name":"薩曼莎·温","primary":false}}]}},"person_5633336_translations":{"at":1774505594067,"data":{"id":5633336,"translations":[{"iso_3166_1":"US","iso_639_1":"en","name":"English","english_name":"English","data":{"biography":"","name":"Peter Jakeson","primary":true}}]}},"movie_525460_credits":{"at":1774505594849,"data":{"id":525460,"cast":[{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":84497,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Aaron Paul","original_name":"Aaron Paul","popularity":3.6344,"profile_path":"/8Ac9uuoYwZoYVAIJfRLzzLsGGJn.jpg","cast_id":1,"character":"Bryan","credit_id":"5b02548cc3a3686c8600f911","order":0},{"adult":false,"gender":1,"id":1186505,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Emily Ratajkowski","original_name":"Emily Ratajkowski","popularity":2.117,"profile_path":"/1YngeK5Bbgw9bu6YG5ZgvCIo4ZX.jpg","cast_id":0,"character":"Cassie","credit_id":"5b02547f0e0a2623bf011fa7","order":1},{"adult":false,"gender":2,"id":59270,"known_for_department":"Acting","name":"Riccardo Scamarcio","original_name":"